    {
      "id": "scene_01",
      "speaker": "我",
      "text": "当我推开实验室沉重的大门时，灰尘在阳光下飞舞。那是她第一次回头看我。",
      "bg": "bg_lab",
      "sprites": { "left": null, "center": "girl_sad", "right": null, "active": "center" },
      "bgm": null,
      "se": null,
      "options": null,
      "next": "choice_01",
      "effect": null
    },
    {
      "id": "choice_01",
      "speaker": "少女",
      "text": "“你...也是来终结这一切的吗？”她的眼神里透着绝望。",
      "bg": "bg_lab",
      "sprites": { "left": null, "center": "girl_sad", "right": null, "active": "center" },
      "bgm": null,
      "se": null,
      "options": [
        { "text": "安慰她", "next": "path_happy" },
        { "text": "沉默地走近", "next": "path_sad" }
      ],
      "next": null,
      "effect": null
    },
    {
      "id": "path_happy",
      "speaker": "我",
      "text": "“不，我是来带你离开这里的。”",
      "bg": "bg_lab",
      "sprites": { "left": null, "center": "girl_happy", "right": null, "active": "center" },
      "bgm": null,
      "se": null,
      "options": null,
      "next": "end_01",
      "effect": null
    },
    {
      "id": "path_sad",
      "speaker": "少女",
      "text": "她低下了头，发丝遮住了眼睛。那是比实验室的空气更沉重的寂静。",
      "bg": "bg_lab",
      "sprites": { "left": null, "center": "girl_sad", "right": null, "active": "center" },
      "bgm": null,
